{"tid":1744581,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 全港黑警淪為condom","createTime":"2019-11-21T22:23:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T22:50:20.000Z","uid":137255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"71285a330d3925305d1d6c064bed377934fa2124","tid":1744581,"uid":137255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:23:14.000Z","msg":"香港戰局無論點完，終有一日都會完。<br />\n完結時，香港要keep住國際金融中心嘅角色，就依然會<span style=\"color: red;\">由<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民官</span></strong>管治 </span>&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n所以到時<span style=\"color: red;\">建制派定民主派執政都好</span><br />\n為左平息民怨同回應國際壓力，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一定會清算全港警甴</span></span><br />\n你地只會係中共同柒婆嘅政治CONDOM<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為光頭警長威完呢幾個月唔使還，<br />\n唔好唔記得香港春袋（中共要嘅錢）係靠國際貿易，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中共唔會蠢到為左保你地30000隻棋 去放棄香港係世界各地撈到嘅錢。</span></span><br />\n香港都係中共隻棋冇錯，但你地成為condom嘅日子已經唔遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有腦自己諗下一歩點自救"},{"pid":"e7a1672200de27eab0f414650f197ddda508643d","tid":1744581,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T22:50:20.000Z","msg":"膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}